<div class="content" name="RefreshedSingleInstance" uuid="4cb5e950-2c61-4a63-bfb9-1c9aa8826d6b"><p>The RefreshedSingeInstance MUST be encoded as a sequence of
bytes representing the following elements of the original <a href="46710c5c-d7ab-4e4c-b4a5-ebff311fdcd1" data-linktype="relative-path">IWbemClassObject</a>, without
any padding:</p><ol><li><p><span>    </span>InstanceHeap
size (encoded as 4 bytes)</p>
</li><li><p><span>    </span>NdTable</p>
</li><li><p><span>    </span>InstanceData</p>
</li><li><p><span>    </span>InstanceQualifierSet</p>
</li><li><p><span>    </span>InstanceHeap</p>
</li></ol><p>The elements of IWbemClassObject are defined in <a href="../ms-wmio/b44d0581-5bd3-40fc-95d7-01c1b1239820" data-linktype="relative-path">[MS-WMIO]</a>.</p></div>